{"id":112920,"type":6,"name":"The Matrix","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5a/72/112920_xVRlo.jpg","rating":{"total":149,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":1,"4":1,"5":0,"6":4,"7":23,"8":57,"9":41,"10":21},"score":8.2},"summary":"　　不久的将来，网络黑客尼奥（基奴李维斯 饰）对这个看似正常的现实世界产生了怀疑。他结识了黑客崔妮蒂（凯莉·安·摩丝 饰），并见到了黑客组织的首领墨菲斯（劳伦斯·菲什伯恩 饰）。墨菲斯告诉他，现实世界其实是由一个名叫“母体”的计算机人工智能系统控制，人们就像他们饲养的动物，没有自由和思想，而尼奥就是能够拯救人类的救世主。 \r\n　　可是，救赎之路从来都不会一帆风顺，到底哪里才是真实的世界？如何才能打败那些超人一样的特勤？尼奥是不是人类的希望？这是黑客的帝国，程序和代码欢迎大家的到来。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>黑客帝国</li><li><span>导演: </span>The Wachowski Brothers(<a href=\"/person/28661\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">The Wachowskis</a>)</li><li><span>副制作人/制作顾问: </span><a href=\"/person/33349\">袁和平</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/35096\">Keanu Reeves</a>/ <a href=\"/person/35097\">Laurence Fishburne</a> / Carrie-Anne Moss / Hugo Weaving / Joe Pantoliano</li><li><span>集数: </span>1</li><li><span>开始: </span>1999-03-31(美国)</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国 / 澳大利亚</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>台湾名称: </span>廿二世紀殺人網絡</li><li><span>港澳名称: </span>駭客任務</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0133093</li><li><span>片长: </span>136分钟</li><li><span>上映时间: </span>1999-03-31(美国)</li>","collection":{"wish":11,"collect":209,"doing":2,"on_hold":3,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"电影","count":42},{"name":"科幻","count":25},{"name":"黑客帝国","count":22},{"name":"美国","count":14},{"name":"1999","count":10},{"name":"欧美","count":7},{"name":"美影","count":6},{"name":"欧美电影","count":3},{"name":"1999年","count":3},{"name":"Warner.Bros","count":3},{"name":"童年回忆","count":2},{"name":"Cyberpunk","count":2},{"name":"异世界","count":2},{"name":"Keanu.Reeves","count":1},{"name":"基努里维斯","count":1},{"name":"Wachowskis","count":1},{"name":"The_Matrix","count":1},{"name":"哲学","count":1},{"name":"经典","count":1},{"name":"映画","count":1},{"name":"攻壳机动队","count":1},{"name":"电视","count":1},{"name":"史诗","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":429646,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/429646","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","commen